      "id": "PopularPost53958",
      "post_content": "The other 4 are clearly enchantments, while a lance should be an artifact. But they didn't have Equipment back in the day. This isn't the last time an enchantment would be made that flavorwise should have been an artifact ([Lashknife](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lashknife), anyone?).",
      "posted_by": "A3Kitsune",
